data.value: Welcome to Group 3 Student Management System - your all-in-one solution for efficient student administration! Seamlessly manage courses, grade and streamline communication between students, and professor. With intuitive interfaces and robust features, our application simplifies tasks such as enrollment, grading, attendance tracking, and scheduling. Stay organized, save time, and enhance collaboration within your educational institution with our Student Management System.
